    <data key="d0">Nielsen Marketing Cloud DataOut Platform</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Jkx6kVbDpL4</data>
    <data key="d2">Handles 250 billion daily events scaling dynamically using Serverless Lambdas and Spark on EMR. Protects downstream systems from API overload using queue-based buffering and smart rate-limiting.</data>
